n is solid. The fallback logic for `production_course` and `theramini_relation` is well-structured. The decision to derive `critique_notes` from `ear_metrics` avoids the need for a new authority file while still providing valuable feedback to the operator.\n","file_path":"sdp/verification/t-025@20260416t054258z-verify.md"}}
